text: János Dalmati (26 February 1942 - 29 September 2020) was a Hungarian racewalker. He competed in the men's 50 kilometres walk at the 1972 Summer Olympics. He was born in Budapest. Dalmati died on 29 September 2020 in Budapest, aged 78. ==References== Category:1942 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Hungarian athletes Category:Olympians for Hungary Category:Racewalkers Category:Sportspeople from Budapest
